         VERSION=1.4.25
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:be8f8e01f4d8c557a8be19212f61774a8fa0f20224b7b5b7a30a027dac971954146f3226e2d92dd9755ce50fa070c576bcc30ca52611dcf807dd077302e3b6a3
